item.title: CVE-2023-32446|2024-10-17T14:12:16.678Z -- dell -- wyse%20proprietary%20os%20%28modern%20thinos%29
item.description: Dell Wyse ThinOS versions prior to 2303 (9.4.1141) contain a sensitive information disclosure vulnerability. An unauthenticated malicious user with local access to the device could exploit this vulnerability to read sensitive information written to the log files.
